The actor couldn’t hide his joy at fulfilling a life long dream of becoming a lawyer. Kanayo has bagged a degree in law Nigerian actor, Kanayo .O. Kanayo has graduated from University of Abuja, UNIABUJA with a degree in Law. The veteran actor took to his social media page to share the good news with friends. Sharing the post, he wrote: “Happening Now. My convocation at the University of Abuja. LLB Bagged. Congratulations to my Coursemate @cutie__patooti, Elizabeth Ayua, 1st First Class in Law, Faculty of Law, University of Abuja. Ya kpotuba, Source